            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "半日收市｜港股半日升58點   蘋概股及晶片股續熱炒",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股半日升58點，大市乏方向，一度跌197點，手機設備股飆，晶片股及AI概念續熱炒。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數半日收報20655，升58點或0.29%，今早開市報20598點，升1點或0.01%。一度低見20532點，跌65點或0.32%，為暫時低位，隨即反彈，最高見20787，升197點或0.92%，</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數半日收報4977，升47點或0.95%，今早開報4926點，跌3點或0.07%；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數半日收報7587，升21點或0.29%，今早以7566點開市，升不足1點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">生物科技指數半日收報8969，升227點或1.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日報20705，升57點或0.28%，高水49點 ; 科指期貨報4987，升43點或0.87%，高水10點 ; 國指期貨報7587，升28點或0.37%，高水18點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">半日成交798.52億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">手機設備股造好，舜宇(02382)半日升8.43%，報78.45元，為表現最佳藍籌股。瑞聲科技(02018)升4.64%，報46.2元；高偉(01415)飛升9.71%，報28.8元 ; 鴻騰(06088)升6.84%，報3.75元；丘鈦(01478)升2.66%，報8.11元 ;    比亞迪電子(00285)升5.56%，報47.45元。手機鏡頭龍頭大廠台灣大立光電昨日公布營收升11%，創同期新高，反映淡季不淡，推動本港上市手機股亦炒上。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：舜宇光學官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中芯(00981)升5.92%報47.35元，升幅居藍籌股第二位 ; 華虹半導體(01347)升4.55%，報26.45元  ; 上海復旦(01385)升4.41%，報17.54元。 </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">AI及DeepSeek概念股造好，閱文(00772)急升7.98%，報29.1元；金山雲(03896)升7.93%，報8.85元；聯想(00992)升4.57%，報11.44元；商湯(00020)升3.03%，報1.7元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"閱文集團2023年度年報封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/00772.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"閱文集團2023年度年報封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/00772.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">閱文集團2023年度年報封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">生物科技股指數大升，聯邦制藥(03933)飆11.74%，報13.14元 ; 信達生物(01801)升6.81%，報35.3元；藥明合聯(02268)升5.66%，報29.85元。    </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">傳統科網股跑輸，百度(09888)半日跌2.79%，報85.35元 ; 美團(03690)跌1.72%，報148.3元，為表現最差兩藍籌股。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源: 聯邦制藥官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/468x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240315_fi_聯邦制藥_SOURCE-WEB_官網.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源: 聯邦制藥官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/468x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240315_fi_聯邦制藥_SOURCE-WEB_官網.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源: 聯邦制藥官網</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14686524-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%8d%8758%e9%bb%9e-%e8%98%8b%e6%a6%82%e8%82%a1%e5%8f%8a%e6%99%b6%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e7%ba%8c%e7%86%b1%e7%82%92",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/HKSTOCK_MIDDAY_source-licensed_fb.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-06 12:20:27",
